    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable daily driver and it\u2019s honestly such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been well-cared for over the years. It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for your next road trip or just zipping around town! I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions. Can't wait for you to see it!",
