    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and its signature individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring an analog and engaging driving experience. The chassis benefits from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and maintains its structural rigidity with the factory carbon fiber roof. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, addressing the platform's primary technical concerns. While the paint displays minor stone chips from high-speed touring, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering linear power all the way to its 8,400 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
