    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily reliability and premium comfort. The engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a consistent service history that ensures peace of mind for its next owner. Inside, the cabin remains clean and inviting, with upholstery that shows only minimal signs of use. While the exterior retains a deep shine, it features the minor, honest imperfections typical of a car that has been enjoyed and cared for. From the responsive handling to the fully functional electronics, every detail has been checked to ensure a turn-key experience. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking quality and longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
