    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and feeling fantastic on the road. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is totally ready to go! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home.",
      "price": 31500.0,
