    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS system. This example is equipped with the tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the rear-drive dynamics are sharp and predictable. Maintained with technical scrutiny, the valvetrain is quiet and the power delivery remains linear across the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. A mechanically honest specimen ready for the B-roads.",
